description._content: Description: Dubai Harbour Improvement Works: Progress Photograph No.15. Loading of Tippers in Drained Pondage Area. Taken Mid April 1960. Location: Dubai, United Arab Emirates Date: April 1960 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/675 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
